import React from 'react'
import { Dialog, DialogTitle, DialogContent, DialogActions, DialogContentText } from '@material-ui/core'
import Button from '@material-ui/core/Button'
import { useDispatch } from 'react-redux'

const AddBookMagazineDialog = ({ openState = false, onCloseCallback }) => {
  return (
    <Dialog open={openState} onClose={onCloseCallback}>
      <DialogTitle>Add Book / Magazine</DialogTitle>
      <DialogContent>
        <DialogContentText>
          Add new book / magazine
        </DialogContentText>
      </DialogContent>
      <DialogActions>
        <Button
          onClick={onCloseCallback}
        >
          Cancel
        </Button>
        <Button
          onClick={() => { console.log('jhjgjh') }}
          color={'primary'}
          variant={'contained'}
        >
          Add
        </Button>
      </DialogActions>
    </Dialog>
  )
}

export default AddBookMagazineDialog
